Package pt.ipp.isep.dei.g312.domain

Class Employee

java.lang.Object
pt.ipp.isep.dei.g312.domain.Employee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Comparable<Employee>
public class Employee extends Object implements Cloneable, Comparable<Employee>
This class represents an employee (collaborator) in the system. It stores essential information about the employee - fundamental characteristics - and a list of associated skills. The class provides methods for accessing and modifying employee attributes, adding skills, and retrieving a list of skills available to be assigned to collaborators. It also implements methods for cloning and comparing employees.
